<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>to<sp/>trigger<sp/>the<sp/>message,<sp/>the<sp/>link<sp/>&quot;cluedo_link&quot;<sp/>must<sp/>be<sp/>at<sp/>a<sp/>distance<sp/>up<sp/>to<sp/>0.25m</highlight></codeline>
