<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>message<sp/>*visualization_msgs::Marker*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">how<sp/>the<sp/>node<sp/>creates<sp/>markers:</highlight></codeline>
