<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#Only<sp/>used<sp/>if<sp/>the<sp/>type<sp/>specified<sp/>has<sp/>some<sp/>use<sp/>for<sp/>them<sp/>(eg.<sp/>POINTS,<sp/>LINE_STRIP,<sp/>...)</highlight></codeline>
